The paper presents a novel variational inference framework for Bayesian sparse Gaussian process regression, which is a topic related to machine learning and statistics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.ST (Statistics). The paper also involves optimization and control theory, which are related to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.IT (Information Theory), respectively.
